item.title: Partials
item.description: Analytics # Blowfish provides built-in support for Fathom Analytics, Google Analytics annd Umami Analytics. Fathom is a paid alternative to Google Analytics that respects user privacy. Fathom Analytics # To enable Fathom Analytics support, simply provide your Fathom site code in the config/_default/params.
